            <title><![CDATA[【🥚#每周吃5个鸡蛋糖尿病高血压风险降低# 】鸡蛋中含有较多的饱和脂肪酸和胆固醇，摄入量不宜过多。近期，美国波士顿大学研究团队在《营养素》上发表的一项研...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【🥚<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E5%90%835%E4%B8%AA%E9%B8%A1%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%AF%8F%E5%91%A8%E5%90%835%E4%B8%AA%E9%B8%A1%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%96%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%85%E9%AB%98%E8%A1%80%E5%8E%8B%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#每周吃5个鸡蛋糖尿病高血压风险降低#</span></a> 】鸡蛋中含有较多的饱和脂肪酸和胆固醇，摄入量不宜过多。近期，美国波士顿大学研究团队在《营养素》上发表的一项研究显示，每周吃≥5个鸡蛋，患2型糖尿病和高血压的风险分别显著降低28%和32%！建议成人每天吃1个鸡蛋，每周不超过7个，避免集中食用。那鸡蛋怎么烹饪更营养？戳<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4990745862406150" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hlv8dued29j21hc0u00ue.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/QMss28Zulx08bMrsU6RG01041200rzHu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705468582&amp;ssig=talMPcW3gM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/W5xdWUBHlx08bMrsulIc01041200eX700E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705468582&amp;ssig=Vbq6Xa7CJx&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/fhIfVcyklx08bMrsbfrW010412009SGi0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1705468582&amp;ssig=MLFqUHWdhw&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4990745862406150" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
